  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Slavers_Bay.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Sea of Sighs is located in Slaver&#39;s Bay\"><img alt=\"Sea of Sighs is located in Slaver&#39;s Bay\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/300px-Slavers_Bay.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/450px-Slavers_Bay.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/600px-Slavers_Bay.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 33.3%; left: 22.2%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Sea of Sighs\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Sea of Sighs</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> and the location of the Sea of Sighs\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Sea of Sighs</b> is an inland sea in central <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. It is south of the <a href=\"/index.php/Painted_Mountains\" title=\"Painted Mountains\">Painted Mountains</a> and north of the <a href=\"/index.php/Lands_of_the_Long_Summer\" title=\"Lands of the Long Summer\">Lands of the Long Summer</a>. At its northeastern tip is the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Mantarys\" title=\"Mantarys\">Mantarys</a>, where a mountain river flows into the sea. Its waters are colored red.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sea_of_Sighs&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Central Essos.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Seas\" title=\"Template:Seas\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Seas&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Seas (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this templa